  "synopsis": "On the first day as a transfer student, Betao comes to meet one girl. Her name is... Kuuki Yominashi! (Her initials \"KY\" mean \"being unable to read the situation/mood.\") When Betao with glasses and Kuuki with skippers meet with each other, the gears of fate starts to spin.\n\nThe contemporary story, intersecting lives; a story of duty, human nature and friendship.\n\nLet's begin the story of a KY-style high school girl Kuuki-chan!\n\n(Source: AnimeBancho)",
